Beesha Abrayn

beesha Abrayn (reer Sheekh Cismaan) waa beel taariikh fac wayn kuleh geeska Afrika. Nasab ahaan waxa ay ka soo jeeddaa beelwaynta Maxamad-Case, Samaroon.
waa Beesha uu ka dhashay Imaam Axmad Guray oo uu magiciisu yahay sidan: Imaam Axmad ben Ibraahim, Ben Axmed ben Cigaal ben Cali ben Cismaan(Abrayn) ben Muuse Ben Maxamad Ben Makadoor Ben Samaroon ben Siciid Ben Daawuud alcaqiily.
Beesha Abrayn waxa ay taariikh facwayn kuleedahay magaalada Saylac ee taariikhiga ah oo ay xaafad gaar u ah ka lahaan jireen xilli ay magaaladu ka koobnayd labo xaafadood oo kala ah: Khoor doobbi, iyo Rawda.
gabayada lagu xasuusto waxa ka mid ah tixdii ahayd (halka Xaramka loo sii maro iyo xaafadda Abraynka). deegaanka Beesha waxa ka mid ah: Saylac, Garbodadar, Geerisa, Farda Lagu xidh, Garaaca, Waraqa dhigta, iyo meelo kale oo badan oo ka mid ah Somali Land, iyada oo ay Djiboutina si ballaadhan u degganyihiin. waxayna u kala baxdaa beeshani todobo qolo oo kala ah: Reer Abokor, reer Axmad Shabeel, reer Aadan Cali, reer Huruur, reer Cali Wayd, reer Cali Oday, iyo reer Gadiid.

